5.3 DUIM-Sheets Module

frame-manager?

Generic function

Summary

Returns true if the specified object is a frame manager.

Signature

frame-manager? object => framem?

Arguments

object
An instance of type <object>.

Values

framem?
An instance of type <boolean>.

Library

duim-sheets

Module

duim-sheets

Description

Returns true if object is a frame manager.
